43100368,,Default,simple,,base,Deluxe Rugged EDA Charging Cradle Bluebird Pidion HM40 HM45,"

The main function of the Rugged EDA Cradle is to power and charge your EDA while your on the move, and hold it securely into position under heavy use.

column2: Suitable for use in cars and trucks.

column1:
• e4 Certified
    Certified to be used in cars and trucks.

• Prepared for permanent installation
    Everything is included to hard-wire the cradle into your vehicle.

The Carcomm Rugged EDA Cradle is the perfect solution to integrate and use your EDA in your car. The unique and patented robust design of the active holder keeps your EDA in place and protects it from being damaged. The perfect holder for the professional user.

Integrated in the holder is an efficient charging circuit, suitable for 12V and 24V, which powers and charges your EDA. The charger is specially developed for professional use where reliability and quality are very important. The charger keeps your device charged and ready for use in- and outside your vehicle.

The cradle is developed to ensure that the EDA is kept in place but is still easy to remove. This is achieved with special fixtures that keep the EDA firmly seated on the cradle connector while driving on bumpy roads. >INSTALLATION
Integrated charging system
By integrating the charging system into the cradle you can very easely built the cradle into your vehicle. Simply remove the cigarettelighter plug and use the included cable with in-line fuse to hard-wire the cradle into the vehicle, no extra accessories are needed.

Installing the cradle
To mount the cradle into the vehicle you can make use of the included rotating swivel-mount. This can be mounted in the vehicle with the included screws. There are also a variety of other mounting solutions available like for example dashmounts, safety-mounts and heavy-duty gooseneck mounts.
